sqls.sql:
SELECT "t1"."订单_ID" "d0",
  "t1"."国家" "d1",
  SUM("t1"."利润") "m0",
  SUM("t1"."折扣") "m1"
FROM "订单" "t1"
INNER JOIN "销售人员" "t2" ON ("t1"."地区" = "t2"."地区")
GROUP BY "t1"."订单_ID",
  "t1"."国家"
FETCH FIRST 20000 ROWS ONLY
